title: (x) Flared stressed sans serif used by Urban Outfitters - History 02 {Tylor Reimer (self)}
content:
I did my best to look around but nothing showed up for this one. Maybe someone knows what it is. It looks possibly like it's from the same time period as Optima.

After some extensive looking around and a little bit of luck, I've found that it is History 02 by Typotheque : [http://www.typotheque.com/fonts/history](http://web.archive.org/web/20131018223235/http:/www.typotheque.com/fonts/history "http://www.typotheque.com/fonts/history")
